title: Did SNL SABOTAGE Elon Musk?
description:
Elon Musk hosted SNL last weekend, and it was terrible even by SNL standards. Could he have been sabotaged? We also look at whether TikTok could be a spy tool for the Chinese government. And did you ever wonder why anyone listens to Bill Gates about anything? #ElonMusk​ #BillGates​ #TikTok​
